original: Mitch loved hole too much for his own good. Unlike most of us who pay the price with alimony and VD, Mitch paid with his life. He had an old lady getting purple puppies on the back of his chopper when they both got hit by a freight train. I can't wait to twist the wick with this guy on the great free ride to Hell.
translated: Mitch为了日批付出了沉重的代价。对我们大多数人来说，这个代价是高额赡养费和性病，但Mitch付出了生命的代价。他的老娘们在摩托后面放了许多紫色的小狗公仔，结果他们都被货运火车撞了。我迫不及待地想和这家伙一起在地狱的路上骑行了。
